Introducing an all new Storehouse! We’ve made it even easier to tell stories using your photos and videos.

• Now available for iPhone and iPad
• Support for photo extensions in iOS 8
• Add #hashtags to your stories and search for #hashtags from the community  
• Find friends from Instagram, Twitter, and Facebook
• New Explore section featuring top categories and trending #hashtags
• Republish your favorite stories to your followers

***2014 Apple Design Award Winner***

Now you can discover more from people you follow and explore stories from our growing community.  

• The stories created and recommended by people you follow populate your Home channel. The more people you follow, the more dynamic your Storehouse experience. 

• See new stories in the Explore channel and get introduced to more members of the Storehouse community.

• The Story of the Day channel highlights one incredible story every day.

• Links can now be added to stories.

• New profile design for easier access to your published stories and recommendations.

• Grid view allows you to see more, faster.

• Drafts are now autosaved to your iPad.

• Fixed the error while attempting to connect to Flickr.

• Other bug fixes and UI enhancements.

If you like Storehouse, please take the time to give us a nice review: it really helps. 

If you run into issues, please get in touch: support@storehouse.co

itunesNotes.standard: Tell amazing visual stories with Storehouse, an app that lets you mix photos, videos, and text in beautiful scrolling pages. Crafting gorgeous sequences is as easy as importing images from your camera roll and other sources, and then arranging the elements any way you like. Share your favorite experiences—scenes from a recent trip, portraits of an old friend—or marvel at the captivating tales posted by other members of the Storehouse community.

description.standard:
***Winner of the 2014 Apple Design Award***

Storehouse lets you tell stories with your photos and videos. 

• Combine photos, videos, and text into one beautiful story.
• Import photos and videos from your Camera Roll, Instagram, Flickr, and Dropbox.
• Share stories with your Storehouse friends and followers
• Embed stories on your blog or share them to other social networks. 
• Explore stories created by your friends and our diverse community of storytellers from all around the world.
• Comment, Like, or Republish your favorite stories. 

It’s never been easier or more fun to create stories and connect with others. 

Need support? Just send us a message at: support@storehouse.co or get in touch on Twitter @storehousehq
